Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory229.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "You're a Corrupted!", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryGanRanNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryGanRanNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "And you're a Corrupted!", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryGanRanNew.prefab', 3: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryGanRanNew.prefab', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Construct', 3: "What's with that Construct...?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Construct Captain', 3: 'I think I saw her on the files before! Are reinforcements coming?!', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Construct', 3: 'Oh! Then we should get ready for a counterattack, yeah?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "NO! Nanami isn't here to help you fight the bionics!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Construct Captain', 3: 'What?!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Answering the Construct, Nanami dashes into the fray, defeating every Corrupted that she sees.'}
{3: "All that stands in Nanami's way is met with a whack of her chainsaw and sent flying afar. Nobody can handle the Nanami calamity."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Staessen', 3: "Oi, Simon, what's with this Construct lass?! Why is she attacking our people?!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Simon', 3: 'I think I saw her with Boss before... Some Construct called Nanami.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Staessen', 3: "I don't need her name! I need a way to deal with that Construct!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Simon', 3: "I'm afraid only our very-not-present Boss can handle her.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Simon', 3: "Soldiers on the frontline, do you copy? Pull back immediately! Don't engage with the Construct that just rushed in.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Staessen', 3: 'What?! What about our defenses?!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Simon', 3: "It'll just be one or two openings. We'll be fine. Getting out of her way is more important.", 4: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 3: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: "We'll cover for the openings.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Staessen', 3: 'Diana... Why are the Forest Guard here? Did you capture that Atiel?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "【kuroname】 and Rosetta will handle Atiel. We've returned to support the frontline instead. Forest Guards, spread out!", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryTongxunHalfNew.prefab', 4: '2'}
{3: "At Diana's behest, the Forest Guard members charge at the battlefield. Taking care to stay out of Nanami's way, they rescue the incapacitated ARU members."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Fisher', 3: 'Pah, took your damn sweet time... some Forest "Guards" you all are!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "But it's still not too late, is it not?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Fisher', 3: '...Whaddya mean?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "Your leg's hurt. Ride on my teammate's back and retreat. We'll handle the rest from here on out.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Fisher', 3: 'Ya think we can leave our defenses to you sinners? You...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "Even if we're sinners... We're sinners born and raised here. Please believe in us.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Martin', 3: "Nanami, at this rate, you'll leave the battlefield. Aren't you trying to pluck all the Corrupted out?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Well, I'm catching the trails of someone that's tryna sneak away!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "Dunno what that is, but that must be the source of all evil! The stinky sneaky baddie that's controlling the Corrupted and making a mess!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: "Martin, you'll have to handle the Corrupted! Nanami is going to...", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Nanami lowers her stance mid-dash, bending so low as if she is about to fall. The angles of her booster wheels adjust and maintain her balance, allowing Nanami to slide forward at full speed.'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: '...Be the hero!', 4: '1'}
